<div class="cards">
	<div class="form-block">
		<h4>会员卡激活确认 </h4>

		<p>请验证您的手机号码</p>

		<%=form_for :card, :url=>"" do |f|%>
			<%=f.hidden_field :no,:value=>@card.no%>
			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label field-label-long">会员卡号 : </label>
				<span class="field-plain"><%=@card.no%></span>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label field-label-long">手机号码 : </label>
				<span class="field-plain"><%=@card.member_card.buyer_tel if @card.member_card%></span>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<%=f.submit "确认提交",:class=>"button submit"%>
			</div>

		<%end%>

	</div>
	<div class="tips-block">
		<p>小贴士</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>如何激活我的会员卡?</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>怎么用会员卡里面的余额付款?</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
	<div class="other-tip "> <span class="required">*</span> 小贴士 :  如果在激活过程中有什么疑问，请致电寻求帮助。客服电话：021 - 22306630 。</div>
	
</div>